data.description: If you are looking for the best house in Cold Springs, you've found it!  This home is full of upgrades inside and outside that makes it by far the nicest home in the area.  A few features include a hot tub and gazebo, gutters with Leaf Filter Protection warranty, decks, observation area, weather station, sheds, fire pit with Solo Stove, RV gate, insulated garage.  The interior walls are insulated and soundproofed, kitchen has granite counters and new title backsplash with a huge island. Feel safe with a complete ADT security system owned. Never have to wait for hot water with continuous circulating hot water and never have to worry about standing water in the backyard, professional plumbing and drains were installed.  The garage has an extra 4 feet of room and an extra 40 amp outlet and it's fully insulated for that workshop.  All garden tools and decorations are included.  This beautiful home has it all and then some!  Check out the upgrade list in documents for ALL the upgrades.
